#============================================================
#   Control script for OpenEJB
#   --------------------------
#    
#   This script is the central entry point to 
#   all of OpenEJB's functions.
#  
#   Contributed by:
#
#    - David Blevins <david.blevins@visi.com>
#    - Daniel S. Haischt <daniel.haischt@daniel-s-haischt.biz>
